          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-home text-[#333333] text-2xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-[#333333]">Regular Cleaning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Consistent weekly or bi-weekly service keeps your Florence home effortlessly maintained. Perfect for busy UNA faculty, healthcare professionals, and families. Enjoy up to 20% recurring service discounts. Your home stays pristine without lifting a finger.
